    entry_requirements = '<div class="accordion__content" id="Entry_requirements-3" style="--panel-height: 144px;"> <p>To be eligible for admission to The University of Notre Dame Australia, all applicants must meet the <a href="https://www.notredame.edu.au/study/applications-and-admissions/admission-requirements" target="_blank">University’s minimum requirements for admission</a>. The requirements for admission are detailed in the University’s <a href="https://www.notredame.edu.au/__data/assets/pdf_file/0027/59634/Policy-Admission-and-Credit.pdf">Policy: <em>Admissions</em></a>.</p><div><p paraeid="{5099f383-a1a6-45cb-8b60-334466211b4e}{133}" paraid="422446705">There are no additional entry requirements or pre-requisites for the Graduate Diploma of Computer Science award beyond the University’s minimum requirement for postgraduate admission.</p></div> </div>',
